@title QIEIdentity
@notice Soulbound identity passport for QIE Neobank
@dev Non-transferable ERC721 with tiered KYC levels
QIE = Quantum Interledger Exchange (fictional) or
      Quetzal Inclusive Economy (if Guatemala-based) or
      Quick Interbank Exchange
Target: Latin America (LatAm) - unbanked/underbanked populations

@notice Initialize supported LatAm countries with ISO codes
QIE focuses on Latin America where neobank penetration is growing
but traditional banking remains inaccessible to many

@notice Issue new identity passport after off-chain KYC verification
@param user Address to issue to
@param tier KYC verification level achieved
@param biometricHash Hash of facial biometrics (irreversible)
@param documentHash Hash of government ID document
@param livenessProof Proof of liveness (anti-spoofing)
@param countryCode ISO country code for jurisdiction
@param validityDays How long until document expires
